e="preserve">Nandi Yellaiah (1 July 1942 – 8 August 2020) was an Indian politician. He was a member of the Indian National Congress party. From 2014 to 2019, he was member of Parliament of India from Nagarkurnool in the Lok Sabha. He was born in Hyderabad, India.
Yellaiah died on 8 August 2020 at a Hyderabad hospital from COVID-19, aged 78.
